title: Frank Lloyd Wright Waterlilies Glasses Set
description:
Depicting waterlilies gracefully floating on tranquil water, our glasses are perfect for entertaining or everyday use. Adapted from an unrealized window drawing by revered architect Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867-1959).

Each set includes four 4 ½ × 3 ½ in. diam. glasses

Care Instructions:  Hand wash only
